<br>
&quot;Well well well...if it isn't, oh what the monacer you go by now, 'Mojo'?  Listen to me, boy...&quot;<br>
<br>
As he reaches up and presses under his chin with his forefinger.<br>
<br>
&quot;::Sarcastic Tone:: I HATE to be the one to burst your bubble, ::now a serious tone:: but the only reason you escaped the Underworld is because I allowed you to do so.  And I don't want you to have illusions otherwise.  Yeah you beat Cerberus fair and square, a feat which very few can do, I'll give you that.  But if I was truly hell-bent against you leaving, you wouldn't have.  So don't allow yourself to be fooled otherwise or become arrogant because you 'beat death'. &quot;<br>
<br>
He then continues to pace around him, awaiting a reaction. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utheerinyes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Erinyes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(4/16/01 10:12:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Tisiphone appeared. . .</span><hr size=1> In a whirl of black flames, Tisiphone, the silent &quot;Freak&quot; Furie appeared standing in between Hades and Mojo. She did not like the fact that Hades was treating Mojo badly. Tisiphone was very close to her Titan brothers and sisters and because Mojo's blood was Titan, she favored him greatly. <br>
<br>
